txt.en: Throne of the Dread Terror: Calm of Death

On the Pelennor Fields, two of the Nazgûl stand guard outside the Causeway Forts. If their vile assault is to be ended completely, they must be banished together at once.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This deed can only be completed on Tier 2 of the Throne of the Dread Terror raid.</rgb>

On the Pelennor Fields, creatures both Living and Dead serve the Nazgûl. They must all be defeated swiftly before their Masters can use them to even worse ends.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This deed can only be completed on Tier 2 of the Throne of the Dread Terror raid.</rgb>
You have completed Challenge: Calm of Death
